00791 static void rna_SpaceDopeSheetEditor_action_set(PointerRNA *ptr, PointerRNA value)
00792 {
00793     SpaceAction *saction = (SpaceAction*)(ptr->data);
00794     bAction *act = (bAction*)value.data;
00795     
00796     if ((act == NULL) || (act->idroot == 0)) {
00797         /* just set if we're clearing the action or if the action is "amorphous" still */
00798         saction->action = act;
00799     }
00800     else {
00801         /* action to set must strictly meet the mode criteria... */
00802         if (saction->mode == SACTCONT_ACTION) {
00803             /* currently, this is "object-level" only, until we have some way of specifying this */
00804             if (act->idroot == ID_OB)
00805                 saction->action = act;
00806             else
00807                 printf("ERROR: cannot assign Action '%s' to Action Editor, as action is not object-level animation\n",
00808                        act->id.name+2);
00809         }
00810         else if (saction->mode == SACTCONT_SHAPEKEY) {
00811             /* as the name says, "shapekey-level" only... */
00812             if (act->idroot == ID_KE)
00813                 saction->action = act;
00814             else
00815                 printf("ERROR: cannot assign Action '%s' to Shape Key Editor, as action doesn't animate Shape Keys\n",
00816                        act->id.name+2);
00817         }
00818         else {
00819             printf("ACK: who's trying to set an action while not in a mode displaying a single Action only?\n");
00820         }
00821     }
00822 }

00824 static void rna_SpaceDopeSheetEditor_action_update(Main *UNUSED(bmain), Scene *scene, PointerRNA *ptr)
00825 {
00826     SpaceAction *saction = (SpaceAction*)(ptr->data);
00827     Object *obact = (scene->basact)? scene->basact->object: NULL;
00828 
00829     /* we must set this action to be the one used by active object (if not pinned) */
00830     if (obact/* && saction->pin == 0*/) {
00831         AnimData *adt = NULL;
00832         
00833         if (saction->mode == SACTCONT_ACTION) {
00834             /* TODO: context selector could help decide this with more control? */
00835             adt = BKE_id_add_animdata(&obact->id); /* this only adds if non-existant */
00836         }
00837         else if (saction->mode == SACTCONT_SHAPEKEY) {
00838             Key *key = ob_get_key(obact);
00839             if (key)
00840                 adt = BKE_id_add_animdata(&key->id); /* this only adds if non-existant */
00841         }
00842         
00843         /* set action */
00844         if (adt) {
00845             /* fix id-count of action we're replacing */
00846             id_us_min(&adt->action->id);
00847             
00848             /* show new id-count of action we're replacing */
00849             adt->action = saction->action;
00850             id_us_plus(&adt->action->id);
00851         }
00852         
00853         /* force depsgraph flush too */
00854         DAG_id_tag_update(&obact->id, OB_RECALC_OB|OB_RECALC_DATA);
00855     }
00856 }
00857 
00858 static void rna_SpaceDopeSheetEditor_mode_update(Main *UNUSED(bmain), Scene *scene, PointerRNA *ptr)
00859 {
00860     SpaceAction *saction = (SpaceAction*)(ptr->data);
00861     Object *obact = (scene->basact)? scene->basact->object: NULL;
00862     
00863     /* special exceptions for ShapeKey Editor mode */
00864     if (saction->mode == SACTCONT_SHAPEKEY) {
00865         Key *key = ob_get_key(obact);
00866         
00867         /* 1)   update the action stored for the editor */
00868         if (key)
00869             saction->action = (key->adt)? key->adt->action : NULL;
00870         else
00871             saction->action = NULL;
00872         
00873         /* 2)   enable 'show sliders' by default, since one of the main
00874          *      points of the ShapeKey Editor is to provide a one-stop shop
00875          *      for controlling the shapekeys, whose main control is the value
00876          */
00877         saction->flag |= SACTION_SLIDERS;
00878     }
00879     /* make sure action stored is valid */
00880     else if (saction->mode == SACTCONT_ACTION) {
00881         /* 1)   update the action stored for the editor */
00882         /* TODO: context selector could help decide this with more control? */
00883         if (obact)
00884             saction->action = (obact->adt)? obact->adt->action : NULL;
00885         else
00886             saction->action = NULL;
00887     }
00888 }
